Summary:
Implemented the full exception hierarchy for gd-tools in src/gd_tools/errors.py.

Classes:
- GdToolsError(Exception): Base class with exit_code attribute (default 2).
  Accepts optional keyword-only exit_code override via constructor.
- ConfigError (exit 2): Configuration errors.
- GodotNotFoundError (exit 2): Godot binary not found.
- GUTNotInstalledError (exit 2): GUT addon not installed.
- CoveragePlanError (exit 2): Coverage plan generation errors.
- CoverageThresholdError (exit 1): Coverage below threshold.
- TestFailureError (exit 1): Tests failed. (__test__=False to prevent
  pytest collection warning since class name starts with "Test".)
- LintError (exit 1): Linting found issues.
- FormatError (exit 1): Formatting issues found.

